      "acceptanceCriteria": "Equivalency between validation experiment input parameters and COU operating parameters must be demonstrated quantitatively at gradation 4.",
      "rationale": "No formal equivalency mapping between the FDA generic pump test parameters and the proprietary VAD COU parameters was produced. Epistemic gap identified. Not assessed."
