    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Credibility assessment accepted for submission purposes under Minimal profile. All 13 credibility factors have been evaluated; 7 factors were formally assessed and 6 remain as documented epistemic gaps at Model Risk Level 5. Achieved levels fall below required levels across all assessed factors, reflecting the high-consequence Class III VAD context. The package is accepted as a complete record of the current credibility state, with the understanding that all identified gaps must be resolved prior to regulatory submission for device clearance.",
